    {
      "chinese": "位於鳥嘴山，也稱上島山北麓的警光山莊溫泉，日本時代設立了「警察療養所」。由於溫泉區北臨汶水溪谷，河谷呈半島形狀，於是日本人又稱之為上之島，故名為上島溫泉。",
      "ab": "ulay na Cinkuwangsancwang ga kiya cku’ ragiyax i’ tagabagan na Camaputing. linuwag na tomuk na Tabilas nku’ Matu’uwal i’ 1908 cu’ kaal. kinbalay na Gipun ku’ Cincalyawyangso i’ 1908 cu’ kaal. tiku ulay i’ Taian na tagabagan ga kiya cku’ luliyung na Mayri’ na uqu’ ku’ quwang na ulay. pantaw ku’ uqu’ ka hani ru sinralu’an na Gipun maha’ Sangtaw. yani ku’ kai’ maha’ ulay na Torayama’.",
      "order": "2",
